{"tid":116211,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"何謂\"左膠\"? 討厭\"左膠\"前先搞清楚自己是否左膠","createTime":"2017-02-11T08:07:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-11T09:04:04.000Z","uid":57723,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4e014d94d9eb7f09a0dd18bc608e6b6e5f83d864","tid":116211,"uid":57723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T08:07:19.000Z","msg":"所謂左膠 意解左翼 加一隻膠<br />\n左翼 意思係支持自由 普世 博愛 大愛 包容思想<br />\nfrom wiki :<br />\n&quot;左派主張積極改革，主張把舊的意識形態和制度革除，從而建立新的意識形態和制度。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n而咩係膠呢 就係雙重標準<br />\n人做得你唔做得 只提對自己論點有利 忽視帶黎的禍害<br />\nfrom 網典:<br />\n&quot;左膠泛指「不現實左翼份子」或「只講理想左翼份子」。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n其實想開post 好耐<br />\n好多人 見人就叫左膠 但左膠係咩都唔知<br />\n見人唔岩key 就鬧左膠<br />\n尤其隔離個屌狗鬧交post <br />\n鬧人左膠 自己卻是不節不扣的左膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e337419613ead064cc3c7edd016fd451323c4195","tid":116211,"uid":57723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T08:09:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a88f2d257211035932c1cabdc442f4f6d604d8c3","tid":116211,"uid":6153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T08:11:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"91f2040ec46cf5f475b0ac6fa1e316a751e32fb2","tid":116211,"uid":57723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T08:11:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b9b768a5c0cbd8309a107dcfbc0d808f891b7a2","tid":116211,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T08:11:38.000Z","msg":"五毛、左膠、港豬呀呢啲只不過係連登仔同人嗌交時屈鳩人嘅用詞嚟嘅啫 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfd4b9c528a7ca3b8ce2b872f14fc8761f376851","tid":116211,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T08:13:39.000Z","ms